<h3>Table Tag</h3>
<p>Tables in Aboitiz Legal utilizes the <code>Data Tables</code> plugin.</p>
<p>Here is the basic view of Data Tables. The table must have an ID and is used on initialization.</p>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-body">
    <table id="table_id" class="abcom abcom-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Column 1</th>
                <th>Column 2</th>
                <th>Column 2</th>
                <th>Column 2</th>
                <th>Column 2</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>Row 1 Data 1</td>
                <td>Row 1 Data 2</td>
                <td>Row 1 Data 2</td>
                <td>Row 1 Data 2</td>
                <td>Row 1 Data 2</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Row 2 Data 1</td>
                <td>Row 2 Data 2</td>
                <td>Row 2 Data 2</td>
                <td>Row 2 Data 2</td>
                <td>Row 2 Data 2</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table><!-- // End abcom-table -->
  </div>
</div>
