<h3>Initialize using Javascript</h3>
<p>Include a <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> tag at the bottom of your HTML document -- before the <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> tag -- and use the following code.</p>
<pre class="yondu__code"><code>$('.abcom-table').DataTable();</code></pre>

<hr>
<h3>Removing other elements</h3>
<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-body">
    <table id="table_id2" class="abcom abcom-table">
