<p>Include a <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> tag at the bottom of your HTML document -- before the <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code> tag -- and use the following code.</p>
<pre class="yondu__code"><code>$('.abcom-table').DataTable({
  searching : false,
  paging : false,
  info : false
});</code></pre>
<p>Here, we used data table options like <code>searching</code>, <code>paging</code> and <code>info</code> for the layout. You can always refer to datatables plugin documentation <a href="https://www.datatables.net/" target="_blank" >here</a>.</p>

